{"tid":2382335,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"資深藝人張錚溫哥華逝世 享年90歲","createTime":"2021-01-27T08:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T07:55:15.000Z","uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"56cf49411bb9654d01596566aaeace0d3050d4d2","tid":2382335,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20210127/s00092/7fb3480604ae74dd8b92a169b0b2c1ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20210127%2Fs00092%2F7fb3480604ae74dd8b92a169b0b2c1ec.jpg&h=8a907cdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20210127/s00092/7fb33eb6f256c13481919ebeeb8d0e51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20210127%2Fs00092%2F7fb33eb6f256c13481919ebeeb8d0e51.jpg&h=4d847971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V8eKFZV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV8eKFZV.jpg&h=7504c94c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張錚（前）1983年與董驃（後）合作麗的劇集《再向虎山行》。（資料圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinakd10100/162/w550h412/20210127/e98f-kicwvzq7895505.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fsinakd10100%2F162%2Fw550h412%2F20210127%2Fe98f-kicwvzq7895505.jpg&h=1f06abc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】資深藝人、溫哥華影視人協會前會長張錚（原名張喬夫）於1月25日（溫哥華時間）在烈治文醫院逝世，享年90歲。張錚在北京出生，曾在上海就讀交通大學機械工程系，因父病故而輟學，輾轉來港於1950年代加入長城影業公司。他參與的電影逾70部，包括國語片《雷雨》、《漁光戀》、《絕代佳人》、《英雄兒女》與《屈原》等。張錚又曾執導電影與拍攝紀錄片。<br />\n<br />\n張錚1970年代加入麗的電視，拍攝劇集《新變色龍》，又與董驃合作《再向虎山行》，還有後期亞視的《上海風雲之爭雄歲月》、《勝者為王》等；1995年拍《九王奪位》後移民加拿大。張錚活躍於溫哥華影視人協會活動，曾擔任會長，他亦有參與演出外地的影視製作，2013年跟楊紫瓊合作拍韓國導演執導的《美味秘方》，又曾回港拍西片《8 Minutes Ahead》。<br />\n<br />\n為人正直 熱心公益<br />\n張錚的死訊傳出，跟他認識的藝人均表惋惜，溫哥華影視人協會形容張錚「為人正直，熱心公益，積極參與影視人協會慈善活動，盡心盡力，對人友善謙卑，是一名不可多得的長輩，我們永遠懷念他。希望張錚太太Grace能堅強地從悲傷中走出，節哀順變」。<br />\n<br />\n歐錦棠在社交網悼念張錚，他說：「張錚是我在演藝行業的啟蒙導師。小時候家裏都愛收看麗的電視的劇集&hellip;&hellip;儘管他永遠一口半鹹淡廣東話，觀眾就只會聚焦在他活靈活現的演技上。」歐錦棠入讀「亞洲電視訓練學院」，就是張錚執教戲劇課程。張錚經常說：「影什麼、像什麼」、 「台上演戲、台下做人」，目的是想學員尊重表演藝術。<br />\n<br />\n娛樂組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/article/20210127/s00016/1611686161293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2Farticle%2F20210127%2Fs00016%2F1611686161293&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn%2BDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=862d265a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2Farticle%2F20210127%2Fs00016%2F1611686161293&h=ecce1ec2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/article/20210127/s00016/1611686161293</a>"},{"pid":"eb8e16764e9786d291629e6aa51b04567f430f87","tid":2382335,"uid":14422,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:13:32.000Z","msg":"十成九藍屍嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60009c6c12d2da83d498c5ab7c9e5d9e467564c2","tid":2382335,"uid":235152,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"eb8e16764e9786d291629e6aa51b04567f430f87","tid":2382335,"uid":14422,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:13:32.000Z","msg":"十成九藍屍嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:16:41.000Z","msg":"無上網大發愛國宣言就算數吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62371cf42032d68fce2b1ce611d35a3511bf4ab1","tid":2382335,"uid":51631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:18:42.000Z","msg":"係時候落去同標叔講馬"},{"pid":"57131ac375ac4315155c83c111120d2454b6a6e5","tid":2382335,"uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:28:12.000Z","msg":"有人擺咗再向虎山行上youtube. 驃叔,張錚,黎漢持,伍衛國,米雪,梁小龍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2dyAW_nZVF0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatc